urls.title: CryptoStykz - Collection
urls.description: ***Join the CryptoStykz Discord Server to battle and bet on your NFTs for weekly prizes!*** https://discord.gg/sH7Ze9faTv CrytpoStykz is an army of unique NFT stickfigures brought together from libraries of legendary Pivot animators of the early-mid 2000's. Fellow animators around the globe will instantly recognize the figures from the highly regarded animations of Jon, Bert, Pistol, and many more... These long lost stickfigures were used in Pivot 2.2.7 animations that shaped peoples' childhoods. Legends were born on the forums DarkDemon and Droidz, with hundreds of thousands of users. Many of them to this day will remember these stickfigures like the back of their hands. The animations themselves can be seen in my other collection DarkDemonz. The history of DarkDemon and Droidz are now saved forever in the Blockchain. I hope this will bring joy to those who see it, and shed light on a hidden, talented community of animators/artists that once existed. Thank you all, -CryptoStykz
